  "keyFeatures": [
    "Voice-to-contract conversion using Whisper AI",
    "Multi-modal verification via SMS, USSD, and voice",
    "Automated mobile money escrow with conditional release",
    "Cryptographic Ed25519 signatures for contract integrity",
    "Real-time WebSocket status streaming",
    "Feature phone and smartphone support",
    "Analytics ETL pipeline for business intelligence",
    "Africa's Talking integration for voice, SMS, and payments"
